<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Template</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #ffffff;
         /* Black background color */
        }
        .container {
        
            background-color: #000000;
            width: 700px;
            padding: 20px; /* Padding from left and right */
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0 auto;
          
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        th, td {
            color: #FFFFFF; /* White text color for contrast */
            text-align: center; /* Center align text */
            padding: 10px;
        }
        .header-text {
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center; /* Center align text */
        }
        .image-container img {
            width: 100%; /* Adjust image width if necessary */
            height: auto;
            margin-left: -10%; /* Adjust to position image slightly to the left */
        }
        .mainContent {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            background: #181818;
            border-radius: 10px; /* Add border-radius for rounded corners */
         
           
            padding: 20px;
            overflow: hidden; /* Ensure content is contained within the border-radius */
        }
        .mainContent td {
            text-align: left;
            padding-left: 30px; /* Adjust padding */
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .mainContent .heading {
            font-size: 30px;
        }
        .mainContent .greeting {
            color: gray;
        }
        .mainContent .thanks {
            font-size: 17px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #9add3a;
            color: black;
            padding: 15px 30px; /* Adjust padding for button */
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px; /* Optional: Add rounded corners to button */
        }
        .mainContent2 {
       
            background: #181818;
            border-radius: 10px; /* Add border-radius for rounded corners */
            margin: 0 auto; /* Center align content */
            padding: 20px; /* Add padding inside the container */
        }
        .mainContent2 li {
            text-align: left;
            padding-left: 10px;
        }
        .mainContent2 .heading {
            font-size: 30px;
        }
        .paragraph{
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 30px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid gray;
        }
        .footer {
color: #fff;
padding: 30px;

        }
        .footer h3{
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-top: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #00ffff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .screen img{
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <table>
            <tr class="image-container">
                <td>
                  <img src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/pixel-pulse-7e4eb.appspot.com/o/images%2F1721846627386?alt=media&token=85c72bc4-02ec-4314-b18f-3496440d13bf" alt="logo" style="width: 170px;">
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="header-text">Your Purchase Confirmation & Download Link for <span style="color: #00ffff;">{{productTitle}}</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="screen">
                    <!-- Image placeholder -->
                    <img src={{productImage}} alt="Purchase Image" style="max-width: 100%; height: 500px; object-fit: cover; object-position: top;">
                    
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <div class="mainContent">
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <!-- Content for confirmation and download link -->
                        <p style="color:#9add3a" class="heading">Welcome <span style="color:#3acadd">to Dipixels!</span></p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="greeting">Hi {{firstName}},</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="thanks">Thank you for your purchase!</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="color:rgb(139, 135, 135); ">
                        We're excited to let you know that your order has been successfully processed. You can now download your purchased theme using the link below:
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-top: 10px;">
                      <p></p>
                        <a href={{productFilePath}} style="font-size: 20px; cursor: pointer;  background-color:#9add3a ; color: #000000; padding-left: 20px;  padding-right: 20px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; border-radius: 20px; text-decoration: none; ">Click Here</a>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
        <ul class="mainContent2">
            <li>
                <p style="color:#9add3a" class="heading">Order <span style="color:#3acadd">Details</span></p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p style="color:rgb(139, 135, 135);">Transaction ID: {{orderTransactionId}}</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p style="color:rgb(139, 135, 135);">Theme Name: {{productTitle}}</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p style="color:rgb(139, 135, 135);">Purchase Date: {{orderDate}}</p>
            </li>
        </ul>


        <p style="color:#ffffff" class="paragraph">
            We hope you enjoy your new theme and that it helps you create something amazing. If you have any questions or need assistance, please feel free to reach out to our support team at: <span style="color: aqua;">support@dipixels.com</span> <br/> <br/>Thank you for choosing Dipixels LLC. We look forward to serving you again soon.
        </p>

        <div class="footer">
            <h3>Best Regards,</h3>
            <h2>Dipixels LLC</h2>
            <a href="https://www.pixelpulse.dipixels.com">www.pixelpulse.dipixels.com</a>
            <p>&copy;2024 Pixel Pulse | All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>